channel.title: [Need] Webclient[317][MayPay]
channel.description:
Well, I know their is a lot of people needing webclients. But I just can't figure it out. I tried everything that I knew, do the best of my ability, so I feel that I got defeated. This is my last resource. Can anyone out there get me a working, stable, good web client for my server, if its good enough, I may even pay up to 5.00. All I want is to get my server going.
Thanks, Krowen.
